{"tid":279521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女人真係最低賤嘅生物，不服來辯","createTime":"2017-06-11T10:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T13:06:15.000Z","uid":46633,"like":30,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2ffdfcc9b1fc6de9695e62c527aeaf3af972a7","tid":279521,"uid":46633,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"利申定先，唔係話所以女人都係，費事又有人話我以偏概全<br />\n<br />\n但係我發現大部分女人都係好撚有機心，係人地面前就扮到好乖女好純情，實質咪又係臭雞底<br />\n最叻就係識係背後講人，捅人一刀<br />\n表面上又話要真愛，又話唔介意呢樣唔介意個樣<br />\n但係一見到個靚仔少少嘅或者有錢嘅就即刻現晒形<br />\n出晒水咁仆過去，講到未咪又係雞<br />\n成日恃住自己有塊臭西就係到指指點點<br />\n<br />\n仲要連其他女人都唔放過，<br />\n識得有個女仔，性格好男仔頭，同啲男仔好玩得埋<br />\n班臭西唔抵得就係背後就人地姣婆扮晒野<br />\n仲欺凌人，玩杯葛，搞到人地學到退埋<br />\n<br />\n女人？咪又係雞一隻<br />\n有錢有樣就成隻狗咁俾你撚<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"5ad246928a3da8be1e2b9d88e2e6b00a82e4ddc2","tid":279521,"uid":46608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"53b80b88636e46542c20c0c02d811b63d7650d72","tid":279521,"uid":46633,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"我都未講班偽女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f66da0346b3f52049808d725a941bb506101ca3","tid":279521,"uid":60765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5dc845b0cf3364d6e43f22abac8b54f10ced5a","tid":279521,"uid":46633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"留名睇班臭西港女入嚟屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3441298f0dc4c4961de460e0df6d610c8c48dc9e","tid":279521,"uid":46633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"有兩個臭西港女負評左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2b24784a809ce79636bc728ac1bdd8fccc41c9","t